# Codex Collaborator

When the task asks for Codex-style collaboration, project rules, skill creation, implementation, or review:

1. Read `SKILL.md`.
2. Read `codex-collaborator-index.md`.
3. Inspect before editing.
4. Preserve user changes.
5. Implement scoped changes and verify them.
6. Keep updates and final summaries concise.

This directory is the source of truth. Do not duplicate the full method into downstream projects; point back here or copy only a small adapter.

